{"tid":2500505,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"私營龕場長霞淨院霸萬呎官地14年 疑前警員任院長 地政不執法更不反對改劃","createTime":"2021-04-22T16:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T00:57:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"67957636a774e60eea82477b8c7d8da3f60b142a","tid":2500505,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T16:35:17.000Z","msg":"《私營骨灰龕場條例》2017年生效，惟發牌進度緩慢，絕大部份私營龕場至今仍未獲發牌，反而造就它們在申請期間的土地違例行為不受監管。《蘋果》調查發現，正在申請牌照、坐擁1.3萬個龕位的私營龕場佛教長霞淨院，除了違反土地用途放置骨灰，更於過去14年一直霸佔1.4萬呎官地作花園。地政總署雖明知長霞涉多項違規，但除9年前一次罰款外，一直都未有執法，早前長霞在城規會申請更改土地用途，地署更表示「不反對」其申請。長霞未售的龕位涉數以億元計的收入，據悉是前警務人員的院長拒絕回應《蘋果》查詢。<br />\n<br />\n根據網站介紹，位於大埔錦山的佛教長霞淨院早於1928年已開設佛堂，起初名為「美全堂」，1960年更名為「長霞精舍」，至2002年再易名為佛教長霞淨院。長霞聲稱自70年代已有營運骨灰龕，但因應《私營骨灰龕場條例》，必須申請改劃土地用途，才有機會獲發牌照。<br />\n<br />\n根據城規會資料，長霞淨院已兩度申請由現時的「鄉村式發展」地帶，改為「政府、機構或社區」用途，以符合私營骨灰龕場的牌照申請，首次申請在2019年7月提出，去年9月已被城規會拒絕，但長霞在3個月後隨即再次遞交申請，城規會將於今年4月30日舉行會議處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210423/LDRPE2XKD5AWDB2BHBVFR727HU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210423%2FLDRPE2XKD5AWDB2BHBVFR727HU%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrcZiPQ%2BZ2BAZCV%2B6nVsqWzo%3D&h=54283a13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210423%2FLDRPE2XKD5AWDB2BHBVFR727HU%2F&h=0b9c5957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210423/LDRPE2XKD5AWDB2BHBVFR727HU/</a>"},{"pid":"ec4a0126f877d545c0c8448e147ce970086a6027","tid":2500505,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"犯法就犯法呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac062b6d4bddcc05add2660a2227c51debdf913","tid":2500505,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T16:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542634acf22d385113d8d5f0d8a95e42335db570","tid":2500505,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T00:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發死人財"},{"pid":"7a1192952a050e80ec2456495ca55333cfc3292a","tid":2500505,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T00:19:29.000Z","msg":"唔單只懶理，仲合理、合法化違法嘅事，附送埋個牌照，等罪犯可以合法、光明正大咁經營。當中，有幾多公職人員行為不當嘅事？咁賣白粉可以幾時領正牌？"},{"pid":"ffc72edcb321f17d9c4a830a948e26c2e49d98c4","tid":2500505,"uid":151540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T00:40:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"becf235a60b00baa4a5f8b14148ac3388a2dc4d5","tid":2500505,"uid":364850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T00:40:17.000Z","msg":"真係同支那狗一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b80497422c75f94807c833446f4e723fec16882","tid":2500505,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T00:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}